e><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/8906e5c97475cd1b0aec5e7449ba59a4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Roberto-Campanella-132x200.jpg" width="66" height="100" alt="Roberto Campanella" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Roberto Campanella"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/roberto-campanella/">View all articles by Roberto Campanella</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/11/don-pasquale-alla-48-stagione-lirica-di-tradizione-del-teatro-g-b-pergolesi-di-jesi/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> &#8220;Don Pasquale&#8221; alla 48^ Stagione Lirica di Tradizione del Teatro G.B. Pergolesi di Jesi</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/11/venezia-palazzetto-bru-zane-festival-edouard-lalo-trio-ceres/" rel="next">Venezia, Palazzetto Bru Zane, Festival Édouard Lalo: Trio Cérès <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementar